<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🎀 Calendrier de {{ child.firstName }} — Grooty</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        :root {
            --hk-pink:      #FF85A1;
            --hk-pink-soft: #FFD6E0;
            --hk-pink-pale: #FFF0F5;
            --hk-red:       #E8355A;
            --hk-yellow:    #FFE566;
            --hk-white:     #FFFFFF;
            --hk-ink:       #3D2B3D;
            --hk-muted:     #B08090;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF0F5 0px, #FFF0F5 20px, #FFE8F0 20px, #FFE8F0 40px);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--hk-ink);
        }

        /* ── HEADER ── */
        .share-header {
            background: var(--hk-pink);
            padding: .75rem 1.2rem;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .8rem;
        }
        .share-avatar { width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);flex-shrink:0; }
        .share-avatar-placeholder { width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0; }
        .share-header-info { flex:1;min-width:0; }
        .share-header-name { font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1rem;color:white;font-weight:400; }
        .share-header-sub { font-size:.72rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-top:1px; }
        .share-header-brand { font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-style:italic;flex-shrink:0; }
        .share-cta-btn { padding:.4rem .9rem;border-radius:100px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);color:white;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;flex-shrink:0;white-space:nowrap; }

        .main { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.5rem; }

        /* ── SEMAINE ── */
        .week-block {
            background: var(--hk-white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 2.5px solid var(--hk-pink);
            padding: 1.2rem 1.2rem .8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(255,133,161,.15);
            overflow-x: auto;
            position: relative;
        }
        .week-block::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 5px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,
                var(--hk-pink) 0, var(--hk-pink) 12px,
                var(--hk-yellow) 12px, var(--hk-yellow) 24px);
        }
        .week-label { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--hk-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

        /* ── RANGÉE ── */
        .train-row {
            display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 6px;
            padding-bottom: .8rem; min-width: max-content;
            position: relative;
        }
        .train-row::after {
            content: '🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸🌸';
            position: absolute; bottom: .1rem; left: 0; right: 0;
            font-size: .5rem; letter-spacing: 4px; opacity: .35;
            pointer-events: none; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* ── KITTY HEAD ── */
        .kitty-head { flex-shrink: 0; width: 100px; margin-right: 6px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
        .kitty-outer { position: relative; width: 90px; height: 90px; }
        .kitty-ear { position: absolute; top: 0; width: 28px; height: 32px; background: var(--hk-white); border: 3px solid var(--hk-pink); border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0; }
        .kitty-ear::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 5px 5px 0; background: var(--hk-pink-soft); border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0; }
        .kitty-ear.left  { left: 6px;  transform: rotate(-12deg); }
        .kitty-ear.right { right: 6px; transform: rotate(12deg); }
        .kitty-bow-ear { position: absolute; top: -6px; right: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; z-index: 3; }
        .kitty-face {
            position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 82px; height: 82px; background: var(--hk-white);
            border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid var(--hk-pink);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(255,133,161,.2); z-index: 1; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .kitty-avatar { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; opacity: .25; }
        .kitty-features { position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding-bottom: 12px; z-index: 2; }
        .kitty-eyes { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .kitty-eye { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--hk-ink); border-radius: 50%; }
        .kitty-nose { width: 6px; height: 4px; background: var(--hk-yellow); border-radius: 50%; }
        .kitty-whiskers { position: absolute; bottom: 20px; left: 0; right: 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 8px; z-index: 3; }
        .kitty-whiskers span { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
        .kitty-whiskers span i { display: block; width: 20px; height: 1.5px; background: rgba(176,128,144,.45); border-radius: 2px; }
        .kitty-name { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: .62rem; font-style: italic; text-align: center; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--hk-pink); margin-top: 4px; }

        /* ── WAGON ── */
        .hk-day { flex-shrink: 0; width: 104px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .hk-card {
            background: var(--hk-pink-pale); border: 2px solid var(--hk-pink-soft);
            border-radius: 16px; padding: .5rem .5rem .45rem;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; position: relative;
        }
        .hk-day.today .hk-card { border-color: var(--hk-red) !important; background: rgba(232,53,90,.04); }
        .hk-day.today .hk-card::after { content: '🎀'; position: absolute; top: -8px; right: 4px; font-size: .7rem; }
        .hk-dayname { font-size: .54rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .07em; color: var(--hk-muted); }
        .hk-date { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--hk-pink); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 3px; }
        .hk-day.today .hk-date { color: var(--hk-red); }
        .hk-event { background: var(--hk-white); border: 1.5px solid var(--hk-pink-soft); border-radius: 10px; padding: .28rem .38rem; }
        .hk-label { font-size: .52rem; line-height: 1.35; color: var(--hk-ink); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 2px; }
        .hk-photo { margin-top: 3px; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
        .hk-photo img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; border-radius: 8px; max-height: 80px; object-fit: contain; cursor: zoom-in; }
        /* Lightbox */
        .lightbox { display:none; position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:300; background:rgba(61,43,61,.88); align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:1rem; }
        .lightbox.open { display:flex; }
        .lightbox img { max-width:100%; max-height:90vh; border-radius:16px; object-fit:contain; box-shadow:0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.5); border:3px solid #FFD6E0; }
        .lightbox-close { position:fixed; top:1rem; right:1rem; background:rgba(255,133,161,.3); border:none; color:white; font-size:1.5rem; border-radius:50%; width:40px; height:40px; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }
        .hk-feet { display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: center; padding: 3px 0 0; font-size: .75rem; }

        /* ── CTA ── */
        .share-cta { background: var(--hk-white); border-radius: 20px; border: 2.5px solid var(--hk-pink); padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .share-cta h2 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: .5rem; color: var(--hk-ink); }
        .share-cta p { color: var(--hk-muted); font-size: .88rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.5; }
        .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem; padding: .65rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 100px; font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; border: none; }
        .btn-primary { background: var(--hk-pink); color: white; }
        .btn-ghost { background: white; color: var(--hk-muted); border: 1.5px solid var(--hk-pink-soft); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="share-header">
    {% if child.avatarPath %}
    <img src="/uploads/events/{{ child.avatarPath }}" class="share-avatar" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
    {% else %}
    <div class="share-avatar-placeholder">🎀</div>
    {% endif %}
    <div class="share-header-info">
        <div class="share-header-name">{{ child.firstName }}</div>
        <div class="share-header-sub">Calendrier partagé · lecture seule</div>
    </div>
    <div class="share-header-brand">Grooty</div>
    <a href="/register" class="share-cta-btn">Rejoindre</a>
</div>

<div class="main">

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.7);border-radius:12px;padding:.7rem 1rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--hk-muted);">
        <span>👁️</span>
        <span>Calendrier de <strong>{{ child.firstName }}</strong> — lecture seule, 2 semaines.</span>
    </div>

    {% set joursFR = {'Mon':'Lun','Tue':'Mar','Wed':'Mer','Thu':'Jeu','Fri':'Ven','Sat':'Sam','Sun':'Dim'} %}
    {% set today   = 'now'|date('Y-m-d') %}

    {% for weekOffset in 0..1 %}
        {% set wStart = 'monday this week'|date_modify('+' ~ weekOffset ~ ' weeks') %}
        {% set wEnd   = wStart|date_modify('+6 days') %}

        <div class="week-block">
            <div class="week-label">
                🌸 Semaine {{ wStart|date('W') }} · du {{ wStart|date('d') }} au {{ wEnd|date('d') }} {{ wEnd|date('F Y') }}
            </div>

            <div class="train-row">

                {# Tête Kitty #}
                <div class="kitty-head">
                    <div class="kitty-outer">
                        <div class="kitty-ear left"></div>
                        <div class="kitty-ear right"></div>
                        <div class="kitty-bow-ear">🎀</div>
                        <div class="kitty-face">
                            {% if child.avatarPath %}
                            <img src="/uploads/events/{{ child.avatarPath }}" class="kitty-avatar" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                            {% endif %}
                            <div class="kitty-whiskers">
                                <span><i></i><i></i></span>
                                <span><i></i><i></i></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="kitty-features">
                                <div class="kitty-eyes"><div class="kitty-eye"></div><div class="kitty-eye"></div></div>
                                <div class="kitty-nose"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kitty-name">{{ child.firstName }}<br>S{{ wStart|date('W') }}</div>
                </div>

                {% for d in 0..6 %}
                    {% set day     = wStart|date_modify('+' ~ d ~ ' days') %}
                    {% set dayKey  = day|date('Y-m-d') %}
                    {% set isToday = dayKey == today %}
                    {% set dayEvts = weekByDay[weekOffset] is defined and weekByDay[weekOffset][dayKey] is defined
                                     ? weekByDay[weekOffset][dayKey] : [] %}

                    <div class="hk-day {% if isToday %}today{% endif %}">
                        <div class="hk-card">
                            <div class="hk-dayname">{{ joursFR[day|date('D')]|default(day|date('D')) }}{% if isToday %} ✦{% endif %}</div>
                            <div class="hk-date">{{ day|date('d') }}</div>
                            {% for e in dayEvts %}
                            <div class="hk-event">
                                <div class="hk-label">
                                    <span>{% if e.type=='garde' %}🏠{% elseif e.type=='activite' %}🎡{% elseif e.type=='medical' %}🏥{% elseif e.type=='vacances' %}🌈{% else %}🎀{% endif %}</span>
                                    <span>{{ e.title|slice(0,16) }}{% if e.title|length > 16 %}…{% endif %}</span>
                                </div>
                                {% if e.image %}
                                <div class="hk-photo">
                                    <img src="/uploads/events/{{ e.image.filePath }}" onerror="this.parentElement.style.display='none'">
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                        <div class="hk-feet">🐾🐾</div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}

            </div>
        </div>
    {% endfor %}

    <div class="share-cta">
        <h2>Vous faites partie de la famille de <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--hk-pink)">{{ child.firstName }}</em> ? 🎀</h2>
        <p>Créez un compte gratuit pour ajouter des événements, écrire des notes<br>et recevoir les mises à jour en temps réel.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:.8rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">🌿 Créer mon compte</a>
            <a href="/login"    class="btn btn-ghost">Se connecter</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;font-size:.75rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.3);">
        Gr<em style="font-style:italic;">oo</em>ty · Agenda familial partagé 🎀
    </div>
</div>

{# Lightbox #}
<div class="lightbox" id="lightbox" onclick="closeLightbox()">
    <button class="lightbox-close" onclick="closeLightbox()">✕</button>
    <img id="lightbox-img" src="" onclick="event.stopPropagation()" alt="">
</div>

<script>
document.querySelectorAll('.hk-photo img').forEach(img => {
    img.addEventListener('click', e => {
        e.stopPropagation();
        document.getElementById('lightbox-img').src = img.src;
        document.getElementById('lightbox').classList.add('open');
    });
});
function closeLightbox() { document.getElementById('lightbox').classList.remove('open'); }
document.addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Escape') closeLightbox(); });
</script>
</body>
</html>
